    • Method Detail

      • execute

        Variable execute(Proces p)
          throws TypeException,
                 LockedException,
                 VariableNotFoundException,
                 FunctionNotFoundException,
                 BreakException
        Execute this block
        Parameters:
        p, - the proces on which the block operates
        Returns:
        null, the result of an operation, an event to send
        Throws:
        TypeException, - thrown if types aren't matched
        LockedException, - thrown if the block tries to acces a locked variable
        VariableNotFoundException, - thrown if the block cant find a variable
        FunctionNotFoundException, - thrown if the block cant find a function
        BreakException, - thrown if the block has to break
